Who is she?

218
00:09:01,837 --> 00:09:04,715
Linda Carroll,
Peter's ex-wife.

219
00:09:04,799 --> 00:09:07,009
That's why they're coming back
to Concord.

220
00:09:07,093 --> 00:09:08,594
She's their next target.

221
