236
00:09:44,463 --> 00:09:46,381
Just shut your damn mouth
and get in the truck.

237
00:09:46,465 --> 00:09:48,383
Get in!

238
00:09:50,302 --> 00:09:51,386
Move.

239
00:10:00,813 --> 00:10:02,898
