since he got out of prison?

259
00:11:31,821 --> 00:11:35,032
No, but we kept
in regular correspondence

260
00:11:35,116 --> 00:11:36,783
after our divorce.

261
00:11:36,867 --> 00:11:41,371
Yeah, his parole officer
said he forgave you?

262
00:11:41,455 --> 00:11:42,873
